cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.SP. 

The paper deals with the problem of decentralized detection with sensors communicating to a central fusion center, which is a common problem in the field of information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of cumulative sum (CUSUM) strategies is a common technique in statistical signal processing (cs.SP) and machine learning (cs.LG). The problem of quickest change detection is also related to the field of mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
